      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-unveils-record-110-billion-buyback-results-beat-low-expectations-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四，蘋果的季度業績和預測超出了溫和的預期，這家 iPhone 製造商公佈了創紀錄的股票回購計劃，導致其股價在盤中交易中上漲 6%。]]></description>
