      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/motorola-solutions-raises-full-year-revenue-view-after-strong-quarter-shares-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩托羅拉解決方案公司週四公佈好於預期的季度業績後，上調了全年收入和利潤預期，導致其股價在盤後交易中上漲 3%。]]></description>
